name: Eye of Something
description:
Flashing and blinking. how many frames per second do you see in? How many frames per second does a chicken experience life in? How about a serpent? What about you? 25 frames  per second or 6000 frames per second? 

What happens to the world around you when you blink? Do you still see it? I think not. Do you still experience it? probably.

What do you think this creature looks like? Just by looking at its eye?

Another NFT will be gifted to everyone who purchases this, on the primary market.
